Manage your domains and contacts.

USAGE:
  scw domain <command>

AVAILABLE COMMANDS:
  contact         Contact management
  domain          Domain management
  external-domain External domain management
  host            Domain host management
  order           Domain order operations
  task            Task management
  tld             TLD management

FLAGS:
  -h, --help                help for domain
      --list-sub-commands   List all subcommands

GLOBAL FLAGS:
  -c, --config string    The path to the config file
  -D, --debug            Enable debug mode
  -o, --output string    Output format: json or human, see 'scw help output' for more info (default "human")
  -p, --profile string   The config profile to use

Use "scw domain [command] --help" for more information about a command.
